&lt;p&gt;**Previous applicants need not apply**&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated individual to provide comprehensive administrative and clerical support to the Elderly Care and Respiratory Departments as directed by the Team Leader and/or Care Group Support Manager. The successful candidate must be able to work using their own initiative, and also as part of a busy team. Good communication skills are essential as the post holder will need to liaise directly with patients, consultants and other hospital staff. A working knowledge of the Trust internal systems would be required for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
